    {
      "id": 26239,
      "category": "researcher",
      "content": "I was able to find an endpoint that would leak advertiser account information by simply changing the 'aadvid' parameter. The leaked information are Email, name, qualification_url_secret, company, phone number, contact email, address and etc. There are certain conditions that needs to be fulfilled in order to exploit this vulnerability.",
